---
// WhyDeepSystems.astro
// A storytelling section pairing a first-person narrative with an
// animated abstract visualization (depth gradient, network flow,
// optimization curve, and quantum-inspired geometry).
---

<section class="why-deep" aria-labelledby="why-deep-title">
	<div class="why-inner">
		<div class="why-copy stack gap-4">
			<p class="why-eyebrow">Why Deep Systems</p>
			<h2 id="why-deep-title" class="why-title">
				The systems I love most are the ones that don’t reveal themselves easily.
			</h2>
			<div class="why-body stack gap-3">
				<p>
					Long before I built optimization engines or studied quantum information, I was learning
					to descend. Technical diving taught me that depth is not danger — it’s discipline. You
					plan for pressure, for uncertainty, for the moment when instinct is not enough.
				</p>
				<p>
					I bring the same mindset to computation. Quantitative engineering, Hybrid AI, and
					decision optimization are, at heart, the same practice: staying calm inside complexity,
					mapping what can be measured, and trusting the model only as far as the model earns it.
				</p>
				<p>
					Quantum computing is the next descent. Different physics, same instinct — go deeper,
					stay honest with the system, and design for what the surface hides.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<figure class="why-visual" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="visual-frame">
				<svg
					class="visual-svg"
					viewBox="0 0 400 500"
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
				>
					<defs>
						<linearGradient id="depthGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
							<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0b1a3a" />
							<stop offset="45%" stop-color="#0a2447" />
							<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#050a1c" />
						</linearGradient>
						<linearGradient id="accentGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
							<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#38bdf8" />
							<stop offset="50%" stop-color="#22d3ee" />
							<stop offset="100%" stop-color="#a855f7" />
						</linearGradient>
						<radialGradient id="glow" cx="50%" cy="35%" r="65%">
							<stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(56,189,248,0.35)" />
							<stop offset="60%" stop-color="rgba(168,85,247,0.10)" />
							<stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,0)" />
						</radialGradient>
					</defs>

					<!-- Depth background -->
					<rect x="0" y="0" width="400" height="500" fill="url(#depthGrad)" />
					<rect x="0" y="0" width="400" height="500" fill="url(#glow)" />

					<!-- Depth pressure lines -->
					<g class="depth-lines" stroke="rgba(120,180,255,0.10)" stroke-width="1">
						<line x1="0" y1="120" x2="400" y2="120" />
						<line x1="0" y1="200" x2="400" y2="200" />
						<line x1="0" y1="290" x2="400" y2="290" />
						<line x1="0" y1="380" x2="400" y2="380" />
					</g>

					<!-- Optimization curve (descending gradient path) -->
					<path
						class="opt-curve"
						d="M20 90 C 90 60, 150 160, 200 210 S 340 380, 390 300"
						fill="none"
						stroke="url(#accentGrad)"
						stroke-width="2.5"
						stroke-linecap="round"
					/>

					<!-- Network / flow connections -->
					<g class="network" stroke="rgba(125,211,252,0.55)" stroke-width="1" fill="none">
						<path d="M60 170 Q 150 220 220 260" />
						<path d="M120 130 Q 180 200 260 240" />
						<path d="M80 300 Q 190 280 300 320" />
						<path d="M180 400 Q 250 340 340 360" />
					</g>

					<!-- Nodes -->
					<g class="nodes" fill="#7dd3fc">
						<circle cx="60" cy="170" r="3.5" />
						<circle cx="120" cy="130" r="3" />
						<circle cx="220" cy="260" r="4" />
						<circle cx="260" cy="240" r="3" />
						<circle cx="80" cy="300" r="3" />
						<circle cx="300" cy="320" r="4" />
						<circle cx="180" cy="400" r="3" />
						<circle cx="340" cy="360" r="3.5" />
					</g>

					<!-- Quantum-inspired geometry: rotating orbit -->
					<g class="qorbit" transform="translate(295 130)">
						<circle r="46" fill="none" stroke="url(#accentGrad)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.9" />
						<ellipse rx="46" ry="18" fill="none" stroke="rgba(168,85,247,0.7)" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(30)" />
						<ellipse rx="46" ry="18" fill="none" stroke="rgba(56,189,248,0.7)" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(-30)" />
						<circle r="4" fill="#c4b5fd" />
					</g>

					<!-- Quantum-inspired geometry: constellation triangle -->
					<g class="qtri" transform="translate(120 420)">
						<polygon points="0,-26 22,14 -22,14" fill="none" stroke="rgba(125,211,252,0.55)" stroke-width="1" />
						<circle cx="0" cy="-26" r="2.5" fill="#7dd3fc" />
						<circle cx="22" cy="14" r="2.5" fill="#a855f7" />
						<circle cx="-22" cy="14" r="2.5" fill="#22d3ee" />
					</g>
				</svg>

				<div class="visual-quote">
					<span class="quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">“</span>
					Complexity is not an obstacle&nbsp;— it is a system waiting to be understood.
				</div>
			</div>
		</figure>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.why-deep {
		position: relative;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}

	.why-inner {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.why-eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		letter-spacing: 0.22em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #7dd3fc;
	}

	.why-title {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 3.6vw, var(--text-4xl));
		line-height: 1.15;
		color: var(--gray-0);
		max-width: 22ch;
	}

	.why-body p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--gray-300);
		font-size: var(--text-md);
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 60ch;
	}

	/* Visual */
	.why-visual {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.visual-frame {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 1.75rem;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 1px solid hsla(210, 80%, 70%, 0.15);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, hsla(var(--gray-999-basis), 0.5), hsla(var(--gray-999-basis), 0.2));
		backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.visual-svg {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
	}

	.visual-quote {
		position: absolute;
		left: 1.25rem;
		right: 1.25rem;
		bottom: 1.25rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, hsla(var(--gray-999-basis), 0.55), hsla(var(--gray-999-basis), 0.35));
		border: 1px solid hsla(210, 80%, 70%, 0.18);
		color: var(--gray-100, var(--gray-0));
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		font-size: var(--text-md);
		line-height: 1.35;
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
	}

	.quote-mark {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-right: 0.35rem;
		font-size: 1.6em;
		line-height: 0;
		color: #a855f7;
		transform: translateY(0.2em);
	}

	/* Animations */
	.opt-curve {
		stroke-dasharray: 900;
		stroke-dashoffset: 900;
		animation: draw 6s ease-in-out 0.4s forwards;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35));
	}

	.network path {
		stroke-dasharray: 220;
		stroke-dashoffset: 220;
		animation: draw 4s ease-out 0.8s forwards;
	}

	.network path:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.1s; }
	.network path:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
	.network path:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.7s; }

	.nodes circle {
		opacity: 0;
		animation: pop 0.6s ease-out forwards;
	}

	.nodes circle:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.6s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 1.8s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 2.0s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 2.2s; }
	.nodes circle:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 2.4s; }

	.qorbit {
		transform-box: fill-box;
		transform-origin: center;
		animation: spin 22s linear infinite;
	}

	.qtri {
		transform-box: fill-box;
		transform-origin: center;
		animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.depth-lines line {
		opacity: 0;
		animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out forwards;
	}

	.depth-lines line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
	.depth-lines line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
	.depth-lines line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
	.depth-lines line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.55s; }

	@keyframes draw {
		to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
	}

	@keyframes pop {
		0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.4); transform-box: fill-box; transform-origin: center; }
		100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); transform-box: fill-box; transform-origin: center; }
	}

	@keyframes spin {
		to { transform: translate(295px, 130px) rotate(360deg); }
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translate(120px, 420px); }
		50% { transform: translate(120px, 410px); }
	}

	@keyframes fadeIn {
		to { opacity: 1; }
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.opt-curve,
		.network path,
		.nodes circle,
		.qorbit,
		.qtri,
		.depth-lines line {
			animation: none !important;
			opacity: 1 !important;
			stroke-dashoffset: 0 !important;
		}
	}

	@media (min-width: 60em) {
		.why-deep {
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}

		.why-inner {
			grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
			gap: 5.5rem;
		}

		.why-body p {
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}

		.visual-quote {
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>

